  "prompt": "Who is Star Lord's father?",
  "response": "Star-Lord, also known as Peter Quill, is a beloved character from Marvel Comics and the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU). His parentage varies slightly between the comics and the MCU:\n\n### **In the Marvel Cinematic Universe (MCU):**\n- **Ego the Living Planet** is revealed to be Peter Quill's father in the film *\"Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2\"*. Ego is a celestial being with vast powers who seeks to expand himself across the universe. This revelation plays a significant role in Peter's journey and the dynamics of the Guardians team.\n\n### **In Marvel Comics:**\n- **J\u2019son (Jason)**, also known as Emperor of the Spartoi Empire, is established as Star-Lord\u2019s father. J\u2019son is an alien from the Spartoi species and has a more prominent presence in the comics compared to the MCU adaptation.\n- **Meredith Quill** is Peter\u2019s mother. She is a human and plays a crucial role in his backstory, both in the comics and the MCU.\n\nIt's interesting to note that while the MCU took creative liberties by making Ego his father, the comics provide a different lineage that adds depth to Star-Lord's character within the broader Marvel universe.\n\nIf you're referring to a specific version or have more questions about Star-Lord's story, feel free to ask!",
